WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.034
Paolyta-B

00:00:03.136 --> 00:00:04.170
I was out of water.

00:00:04.304 --> 00:00:05.839
Black pool water is really dirty

00:00:05.872 --> 00:00:07.474
and can clog filters badly.

00:00:07.741 --> 00:00:10.110
I use a Sawyer filter and two water bags 

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:11.978
Evernew 2-liter bags.

00:00:12.145 --> 00:00:15.815
The trick: use an adapter screw
 to coupling filter with bags,

00:00:15.882 --> 00:00:19.085
and set up gravitational filtering
instead of squeezing.

00:00:19.252 --> 00:00:23.456
Hang it and let gravity work - 
very dirty water becomes relatively clean.

00:00:23.723 --> 00:00:25.492
Drinkable without boiling.

00:00:25.692 --> 00:00:29.729
At least I had not any stomach difficulties
due to drinking bad water.

00:00:29.929 --> 00:00:31.264
I tried various filters 

00:00:31.331 --> 00:00:34.734
Katadyn BeFree
is useless for high mountain trips in Taiwan,

00:00:34.734 --> 00:00:36.002
it clogs terribly.

00:00:36.169 --> 00:00:40.340
but the best is  biggest classic filter - 
Sawyer SP129.

00:00:40.407 --> 00:00:44.844
Just remember to flush it in reverse
with clean water after each trip.

00:00:45.011 --> 00:00:49.516
And don't let your filter freeze - put it
in your sleeping bag during winter nights.

00:00:49.582 --> 00:00:50.784
Same with electronics -

00:00:50.850 --> 00:00:54.120
keep your phone and any batteries
in your sleeping bag too.

00:00:54.154 --> 00:00:57.157
but put it in airplane mode
to preserve the battery.

00:00:57.190 --> 00:00:58.558
NO MORE BAMBOO!!

00:00:58.658 --> 00:00:59.859
huh?

